# Drop this .envrc into a per-customer directory.
#
# Pick the profile this directory should use. The runtime profile (cookies,
# MS Teams session, history) is stored locally in ./.browser-profiles/<name>,
# so each customer directory is fully isolated.
#
#   use flake .#acme        # -> provides `web` (and `browser-acme`)
#
# Or reference the flake by URL if this dir isn't inside the flake repo:
#   use flake "github:YOU/main-browser-profiles#acme"
#
# Then just run `web` in this directory.

use flake .#personal
